<div id="submissions-tracking" class="docs-section">
  <h2>Submissions & Tracking</h2>
  <p>The Submissions page lets you view and track all forms you've submitted or have access to review.</p>

  <h3>Viewing Submissions</h3>
  <p>Open <strong>Submissions</strong> from the profile dropdown. Your submissions are listed with their current status, form type, and submission date.</p>

  <h3>Filtering</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Form Type</strong> &mdash; filter by a specific form.</li>
    <li><strong>Status</strong> &mdash; show only pending, approved, or denied submissions.</li>
    <li><strong>Date Range</strong> &mdash; narrow results to a specific time period.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Saved Searches</h3>
  <p>After applying filters, click <strong>Save Search</strong> to bookmark that filter combination. Saved searches appear as quick-access buttons above the results so you can reapply them with one click.</p>

  <h3>Status Meanings</h3>
  <div class="docs-card">
    <h4>Pending</h4>
    <p>The form has been submitted and is awaiting review or approval.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="docs-card">
    <h4>Approved</h4>
    <p>The form has been reviewed and approved by the assigned approver.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="docs-card">
    <h4>Denied</h4>
    <p>The form was denied. Check the submission details for the reason provided.</p>
  </div>
</div>
